PLACEHOLDER — no release signing key is configured yet.

Replace this file with the public half of the Optikk release key, then commit it:

    scripts/gen-release-key.sh

Until this file holds a real PEM-encoded ECDSA public key, `optikk update`
fails closed: it refuses to install anything rather than installing something
it cannot verify. See scripts/gen-release-key.sh for the key ceremony.
